quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  75,31,Iye sanali kuvomereza chilungamo kapena kupemphera
  75,32,Koma m’malo mwake adakana choonadi ndi kubwerera m’mbuyo
  75,33,Ndipo iye anapita kubanja lake monyada ali kudziyamikila yekha
  75,34,Tsoka kwa iwe. Ndiponso tsoka kwa iwe
  75,35,"Kachiwiri tsoka lili pafupi ndi iwe, tsopano tsoka lili pafupi"
  75,36,Kodi munthu amaganiza kuti tidzangomulekerera kuti azichita chilichonse chimene afuna
  75,37,Kodi iye sanali dontho la umuna limene lidatuluka
  75,38,Ndipo iye adakhala kam’bulu ka magazi. Ndipo Mulungu adamuumba ndipo adamukonza m’maonekedwe okongola
  75,39,"Ndipo adamulenga m’mitundu iwiri, mwamuna ndi mkazi"
  75,40,Kodi Iye alibe mphamvu yopereka moyo kwa anthu akufa